# WebSocket connection testing
python tests/websocket_test.py
```

### Integration Testing
```bash
# Full stack testing
pytest tests/integration/ -v

# Database migrations
alembic upgrade head

# API endpoint testing
pytest tests/api/ -v --cov
```

